            <thetext>XHR Level 1 did not support uploading files. To work-around, the IFrame transport was introduced. The new transport does not include the IFrame transport yet. XHR Level 2 introduced the upload attribute which may offer this feature and make the IFrame transport obsolete.

My guess is that adding a file object to the form data may do the trick.

Also see:

http://www.w3.org/TR/XMLHttpRequest2/#the-upload-attribute 

http://www.google.com/events/io/2011/sessions/html5-showcase-for-web-developers-the-wow-and-the-how.html.

https://developer.mozilla.org/En/XMLHttpRequest/Using_XMLHttpRequest#Using_FormData_objects</thetext>
